# Drizzle ORM Rules

- Use Drizzle ORM for all database access.
- Define schemas and models explicitly and keep them up to date.
- Prefer type-safe queries and avoid raw SQL when possible.
- Validate all input data before database operations.
- Organize models and queries by domain or feature.
